								</ul>

								<div>
									<label>
										<input type="radio" name="stdPlan" value="Yearly">
										Yearly - $ (Valid for one year, rental only)
									</label>
								</div>
								<p>The call charges are:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Local: 60 cents / minute</li>
									<li>STD: $1.75 / minute</li>
